aces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恆景會去煌極食蛋包飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22016237bbf9b1bfed0c5cfc0c9fe8dcb4f1b3b8","tid":205583,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n以前讀書成日去葵芳食飯<br />\n間唔中去鄧媽媽/小雨天食水餃<br />\n宜家好撚貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恆景之前有間譚仔 地方算大<br />\n但食飯時間勁多學生/OL<br />\n宜家仲搬埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人覺得鄧媽媽好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恆景會去煌極食蛋包飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鄧媽媽okay啦 學生價30蚊有麵又多餸又有野飲<br />\n宜家加到成50蚊已經無再去食<br />\n葵廣入面間新釗記都幾好食<br />\n不過有少少貴"},{"pid":"a7523191a5c22e1dba478f3d140be48ee429eca9","tid":205583,"uid":30762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>陽光啲咖喱牛腩飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哇正 仲有得打機</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係網吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係網吧，個間陽光有好多波仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係有間茶記叫陽光咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n七仔隔離"}]}